<p>l. 2, <foreign lang="grc">συμαχον</foreign> P1, P2 </p>
<p>l. 4, <foreign lang="grc">ΕΛΕΥΘ</foreign> P1, <foreign lang="grc">ἐλευθε</foreign>- P2 </p>
